 NewDad 的 Julie Dawson 谈单飞、获得 The Cure 的认可以及乐队的下一步计划https://www.nme.com/news/music/newdads-julie-dawson-interview-solo-bottom-of-the-pool-the-cure-new-album-3795631?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=newdads-朱莉·道森专访泳池底部治愈新专辑独奏Andrew TrendellFri, 20 Sep 2024 13:23:41 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNewsNME RadarIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3795631 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="朱莉·道森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手向 NME 讲述了在个人首张专辑《Bottom Of The Pool》中受到马男波杰克 (BoJack Horseman) 的启发、他们支持 The Cure 的梦想，以及 NewDad 的“流行音乐倾向”下一张专辑的进展</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newdads-julie-dawson-interview-solo-bottom-of-the-pool-the-cure-new-album-3795631">NewDad 的 Julie Dawson 讲述了独奏、获得 The Cure 的批准以及乐队的下一步计划，该</a>文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="朱莉·道森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Julie-Dawson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/newdad">NewDad</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julie-dawson">Julie Dawson</a>向<em>NME</em>讲述了她的首张个人专辑《Bottom Of The Pool》，以及乐队的下一步计划以及获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/THE-CURE">The Cure</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-smith">Robert Smith</a>认可意味着什么。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-newdad-interview-madra-3558685">封面：未来属于 NewDad</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位来自戈尔韦乐队的歌手即将迎来重要的一年的结束，他在一月份发行了 NewDad 广受好评的首张专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/newdad-band-debut-album-madra-review-radar-3573726">Madra</a> ”，被认为是<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/best-albums-of-2024-so-far-3767987">迄今为止今年最好的专辑之一</a>，并完成了包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newdad-interview-the-cure-cover-album-two-radar-3772058">一站在</a>内的大规模巡演<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newdad-interview-the-cure-cover-album-two-radar-3772058">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>。</p><p> “这真的很有趣，”道森说。 “我们必须去很多我们从未去过的新地方。虽然很累，但这确实是一个美好的夏天。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="朱莉·道森 - 愚蠢的小歌" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sWQDIiTnfRU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该乐队还在亚洲取得了成功， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newdads-album-cover-goes-viral-in-china-as-fans-share-their-own-versions-3751334">中国歌迷通过创作和分享自己的版本，使他们的专辑艺术作品迅速走红</a>。 “那太疯狂了！”道森谈到这一现象时说道。 “有趣的是，这张专辑现在比刚发行时更受关注。”</p><p>虽然乐队的明星可能仍在冉冉升起，但道森在专辑之间抽出时间创作了她的首张个人唱片“Bottom Of The Pool”。她与电子制作人杰克·哈米尔（又名“空间维度控制器”）合作。</p><p>请查看下面我们对 Dawson 的完整采访，她向我们讲述了受到<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/bojack-horseman"><em>《马男波杰克》</em></a>的启发，以及乐队“偏流行”的下一张专辑的进展。</p><p> <strong><em>NME</em> ：你好朱莉。我们最后一次见到你是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/newdad-koko-london-live-review-photos-setlist-radar-3598012">NewDad 在伦敦 KOKO 举办一场史诗般的演出</a>时。</strong></p><p><strong>朱莉·道森</strong>：“那太棒了。当我听说要进行舞台设计和木偶时，我吓坏了。”</p><p><strong>你翻唱了 The Cure 的《Just Like Heaven》，非常棒。您有罗伯特·史密斯的反馈吗？</strong></p><p> “他确实转发了这条推文，这对我们来说是非常激动人心的一天。我听说了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-launch-secret-songs-of-a-lost-world-website-and-whatsapp-channel-3794283">新专辑[&#39;Songs Of A Lost World</a> &#39;]。这非常令人兴奋，我已经等不及了。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C4LQh_GolLD/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852