href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-scotland-glasgow-west-68656073">加里（Gary）是八英尺高的玻璃纤维大猩猩 - 被苏格兰卡洛克（Reynard Garden）偷走了</a>。</p><p> Blossoms首先在音乐录影带中向故事致敬，因为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-everton-manager-sean-dyche-hire-blossoms-for-a-gorilla-heist-in-new-video-for-what-can-i-say-after-im-sorry-3752632">“对不起后我能说什么？”</a> ，看到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rick-astley">里克·阿斯特利（Rick Astley）</a>和肖恩·戴奇（Sean Dyche）的客人露面。</p><p>后来，他们在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blossoms-announce-new-album-gary-with-uplifting-title-track-preorder-listen-3762037">新专辑的标题曲目</a>中再次引用了该项目。在6月分享的那个单曲锯的音乐录影带重新扮演了他作为上述花园中心所有者的角色。</p><p>奥格登（Ogden）在描述该项目时说：“这张唱片的核心是我们五个人在几年中第一次一起录制在房间里。我们想捕捉五个朋友决定创办乐队并一起制作音乐时的能量。” </p><figure id="attachment_3762042" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3762042" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3762042" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/blossoms-Gary-artwork@2000x2000.jpg" alt="Blossoms&#39;Gary&#39;专辑艺术品。" width="2000" height="2003" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/blossoms-Gary-artwork@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/blossoms-Gary-artwork@2000x2000-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/blossoms-Gary-artwork@2000x2000-400x401.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/blossoms-Gary-artwork@2000x2000-800x801.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/blossoms-Gary-artwork@2000x2000-696x697.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/blossoms-Gary-artwork@2000x2000-1392x1394.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/blossoms-Gary-artwork@2000x2000-1068x1070.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3762042" class="wp-caption-text"> Blossoms&#39;Gary&#39;专辑艺术品。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>Blossoms <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blossoms-tease-new-music-via-a-mysterious-hotline-3761586">在6月初开始取笑新音乐，当时他们鼓励歌迷打电话给神秘的热线</a>。 Stockport独立摇滚歌手通过视频宣传了该号码，其中包括一辆拖车，沿着道路驾驶，后端带有巨大的大猩猩雕像，以及数字。</p><p>这一消息也发表在他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/club-nme-all-the-action-from-blossoms-big-night-in-manchester-3586129">2月份将NME标题为NME</a>之后。</p><p>最近，乐队宣布了将于今年晚些时候举行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blossoms-announce-five-nights-in-manchester-residency-for-november-3794201">“曼彻斯特五个晚上”</a>的详细信息。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fblossoms-tickets%2Fartist%2F2097211" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到剩余的门票。</p><p> 《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-blossoms-enlist-famous-garys-to-promote-new-album-3795620">邮报》的开花吸引了著名的加里斯宣传新专辑，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
